          <h5 class="card-title body-2-medium text-color-secondary">
            Tehnology Consultation
          </h5>
          <p class="card-text body-1-regular text-color-tertiary fs-5">
            Our technology consultation services are designed to empower businesses, 
            providing expert guidance and strategic insights to drive innovation and growth.
            Our consultants bring a wealth of experience across various industries,
            offering solutions to address your specific needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-2">
      <div class="card width-card shade border-0">
        <div class="service-image-size d-flex justify-content-center">
          <Image class="img-fluid cloud-image" src={cloud} alt="logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title body-2-medium text-color-secondary">
            Cloud Infrastructure
          </h5>
          <p class="card-text body-1-regular text-color-tertiary fs-5">
            We redefine scalability, reliability, and efficiency through cutting-edge cloud infrastructure solutions. 
            Our expertise lies in architecting, 
            deploying, and managing cloud environments that suit your business needs. 
            We can craft robust and scalable infrastructure solutions on leading cloud platforms
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
